link_mentions.page: Great Britain at the 2012 Summer Olympics
Table tennis at the 2012 Summer Olympics – Women's team

response: In April she reached her best ever ranking, rising from 251 to 211 after her World Championship participation. At the 2012 ITTF Spanish Open held in Almeria, Spain, she lost to the Irish Na Liu 4–0 and Japanese Misaki Morizono 4–1 in the singles qualifications groups and played in doubles with the Spaniard Marina Rodriguez and lost to Singaporeans Li Jiawei and Sun Beibei.
